+				"Recipients are GPG keys that are allowed to decrypt secrets.",
+			Subcommands: []*cli.Command{
+				{
+					Name:  "add",
+					Usage: "Add a recipient",
+					Description: "" +
+						"This command adds a new recipient to a store. " +
+						"A recipient can be a GPG key ID or an email address. " +
+						"If your GPG key is not in the default keyring (like on macOS when " +
